    <text id="A6324T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Evans writes briefly to Sibert to explain why he could not send a letter earlier
                    and announces he will be visiting Sunday.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1868-12-17">Dec 17 1868</date>
                        <name type="place">Staunton</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>My Dear Mollie</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>My love I have just time to write you a line. I will be up Sunday if I live I
                    would have written to you on last Tuesday but Johnny Noon was out of town
                    &amp; I Could not have Sent it he just got back a few moments ago &amp;
                    told me he would send this up. I love you with all my heart &amp; Soul all
                    are well send love to you all my love to all Good bye</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Yours Loving</salute>
                    <signed>D H Evans</signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
